<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٩٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٥٢٧٦ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بَكْرٍ قَالَ:</span> نا سَلَّامٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الْعَلَاءِ بْنِ الْمُسَيِّبِ قَالَ:</span> قَالَ رَجُلٌ لِعَطَاءٍ: أُقَرِّدُ بَعِيرِي وَأَنَا مُحْرِمٌ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«نَعَمْ، قَدْ فَعَلَ ذَلِكَ ابْنُ عُمَرَ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>